make sure to create a ".env" file which include the API's for both telegram and gemini API.
also create a chat_history.json file for chatbot messages handling.
For geminimage create a "images" folder in the directory.
Extract the stickers Folder in the directory for the chat API.
For hosting the bot 24/7 use replit and uptime robot for monitoring the server.

